{"tid":1577453,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"Figure討論(42) 黑狗不可饒恕","createTime":"2019-09-17T16:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T14:55:44.000Z","uid":226524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9cace06777f6a939fdbb28da81dff60be5f876e3","tid":1577453,"uid":226524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vwPVT4W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvwPVT4W.jpg&h=b02536af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HntPfNQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHntPfNQ.jpg&h=df9cb3a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.邊度睇figure 情報 ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://figsoku.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffigsoku.net%2F&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5LZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=8d37f9d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://figsoku.net/</a> (日本)<br />\n<a href=\"http://figurenews.blog.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffigurenews.blog.jp%2F&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5LZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=ebf7e6d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://figurenews.blog.jp/</a> (日本)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.moeyo.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.moeyo.com%2F&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5LZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=b2245cac\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.moeyo.com/</a> (日本)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hobby.dengeki.com/event/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhobby.dengeki.com%2Fevent%2F&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5LZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=4a65f9e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hobby.dengeki.com/event/</a> (日本)大型展覽會 會報導下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.taghobby.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.taghobby.com%2F&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5LZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=51775aea\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.taghobby.com/</a>(香港)<br />\n都係講figure 有得睇埋發售時間表<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://fig-ad.com/?site=1&amp;sort=release&amp;q=&amp;date=201802&amp;category=1001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffig-ad.com%2F%3Fsite%3D1%26sort%3Drelease%26q%3D%26date%3D201802%26category%3D1001&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5LZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=cc5d6d67\" target=\"_blank\">http://fig-ad.com/?site=1&amp;sort=release&amp;q=&amp;date=201802&amp;category=1001</a>(日本）<br />\n呢個就跟日本Amazon 出貨時間<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://myfigurecollection.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyfigurecollection.net%2F&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5LZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=8f05834a\" target=\"_blank\">https://myfigurecollection.net/</a>(歐美)<br />\n幾好用嘅database,可以整理訂單,查埋出貨時間,產品資訊,又有討論區<br />\n<br />\n2. Figure分類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n景品，即係夾公仔機/抽獎活動獎品，呢度通常係指硬膠figure，唔係毛巾，毛公仔之類。價錢平，但易走樣，易見分模線，上色麻麻地<br />\n<br />\n一番賞，即係抽獎最高級獎品，First prize, 質素介乎景品同PVC之間，造工，價錢飄忽，隨時炒貴，一樣有分模線，上色問題<br />\n<br />\nPVC，唔係指原材料PVC膠，係指主流見到嘅完成品FIGURE。視乎邊間公司，一般用料同細節都比景品好好多。<br />\n<br />\nGK，Garage Kit，即係素件，買返黎自己組裝上色。日本Y拍價錢可以好貴"},{"pid":"de23a7a964faeae1fe9caaa4f6092bf3601a1e72","tid":1577453,"uid":226524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:54:31.000Z","msg":"比你搶咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91cbed0a4f4e6f76003054928b56178f76bba13c","tid":1577453,"uid":188772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:56:55.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2410affcad11bfb3926